---
title: Garlicky Prawns & Beans with Roasted Potatoes, Mayo and Tomato Salad
description: This recipe was inspired by a recent trip Chef Jesse took to Spain where she sampled lots of delicious tapas and came home wanting to recreate all of them! Crunchy green beans, garlicky prawns and gold and crispy roast potatoes are the perfect flavour combination, whilst the tomato salad keeps things really lovely and fresh. Enjoy with a glass of wine and imagine you’re in a Spanish tapas bar...!
